Package criticalpath

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CriticalPathGraph
    Represents the critical path network as a whole.
    Task
    Represents a task/activity to be stored in a critical path network.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DuplicateTaskException
    An exception to be thrown a task to be added to a graph is already in the graph (or a task in the graph has the same id)
    InvalidTaskDeleteException
    An exception to be used when a start/end task is attempted to be deleted.
    TaskNotFoundException
    An exception to be thrown if a task is not found to be in a critical path network
